Class DiscordClock

  • java.lang.Object
    • DiscordClock

  • class DiscordClock
extends java.lang.Object
    DiscordClock contains values for a clock in/out message. Values are as follows:
    type = "In" or "Out".
    message = The clock in/out message from Discord.
    calendar instance needed for the Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY and Calendar.MINUTE of the clock.
    time = The time of the clock in quarter hours.
